For Trees, we index using a breadth-first approach.

```dot
digraph "Tree indexes" {
  rankdir=TD;
  size="8,5"

  node [shape     = circle
        style     = "solid,filled"
        color     = black
        fixedsize = shape
        fillcolor = invis];

